py-0.5 font-medium text-xs bg-console-error/10 text-console-error border-console-error/20">✗ Denied</span></div><p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">Required to install system packages and modify system configurations</p><div class="mt-2 rounded-md border border-border bg-secondary/50 p-3"><p class="font-mono text-muted-foreground text-xs">You will be prompted for your password when needed</p></div></div><div class="flex-shrink-0"><button class="inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center whitespace-nowrap font-medium text-sm outline-none transition-all focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-[3px] focus-visible:ring-ring/50 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 aria-invalid:border-destructive aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 [&amp;_svg:not([class*='size-'])]:size-4 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 border bg-background shadow-xs hover:bg-accent hover:text-accent-foreground dark:border-input dark:bg-input/30 dark:hover:bg-input/50 h-8 gap-1.5 rounded-md px-3 has-[&gt;svg]:px-2.5" data-slot="button">Mark as Done</button></div></div></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-3 border-b pb-6 last:border-b-0 last:pb-0"><div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3"><div class="min-w-0 flex-1"><div class="mb-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2"><h3 class="font-medium text-foreground">Full Disk Access</h3><span class="rounded-md border px-2 py-0.5 font-medium text-xs bg-secondary text-muted-foreground border-border">○ Pending</span></div><p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">Recommended for complete system management capabilities</p><div class="mt-2 rounded-md border border-border bg-secondary/50 p-3"><p class="font-mono text-muted-foreground text-xs">First make sure nixmac is in your Applications folder (not running from the install disk image). Then go to System Settings → Privacy &amp; Security → Full Disk Access and add nixmac to the list.</p></div></div><div class="flex-shrink-0"><button class="inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center whitespace-nowrap font-medium text-sm outline-none transition-all focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-[3px] focus-visible:ring-ring/50 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 aria-invalid:border-destructive aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 [&amp;_svg:not([class*='size-'])]:size-4 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 border bg-background shadow-xs hover:bg-accent hover:text-accent-foreground dark:border-input dark:bg-input/30 dark:hover:bg-input/50 h-8 gap-1.5 rounded-md px-3 has-[&gt;svg]:px-2.5" data-slot="button">Mark as Done</button></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex items-center justify-between"><p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">Grant all required permissions to continue</p><button class="inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap font-medium text-sm outline-none transition-all focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-[3px] focus-visible:ring-ring/50 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 aria-invalid:border-destructive aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 [&amp;_svg:not([class*='size-'])]:size-4 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 bg-primary text-primary-foreground hover:bg-primary/90 h-10 rounded-md px-6 has-[&gt;svg]:px-4" data-slot="button" disabled="">Continue to Console</button></div><div class="rounded-lg border p-4 border-border bg-secondary/30 mt-6"><div class="flex gap-3"><div class="mt-0.5 size-5 flex-shrink-0 text-primary"><svg aria-label="Information" class="size-full" fill="none" role="img" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><title>Information</title><path d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"></path></svg></div><div class="flex-1"><h4 class="mb-1 font-medium text-sm">Why does nixmac need these permissions?</h4><p 